Attilla/Luzbel:

Attilla and Luzbel increased their speed and was behind to Preborn

--- In nbwrpg@y..., "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> Prebon moved quickly, pushing his jetpack to its limits, the two 
dragons were still behind him but it was his pride that made him 
push. He fealt it necessary to make sure that he reached the Black 
Fortress before they did.He was to the SouthEast of  Greece when he 
detected two signals moving in his direction useing his personal 
frequency. He stopped, curious about how and why bots on this planet 
would be useing such basic frequencies. "Go on ahead, I'll catch up 
to you." He radio'd back to Attilah and Kali.  He reset his course 
south on an intercept course. The Predacon Trainer wanted to see for 
himself just what he was dealing with.
